OL,3,CWidows secure 'significant' settlement
OL,4,Cover paramilitary killings 'collusion'
OL,6,FThe widows of two men murdered by
OL,7,Floyalist paramilitaries nearly 48
OL,8,Fyears ago have secured "significant"
OL,9,Fsettlements in legal actions against
OL,10,Fthe police and Ministry of Defence
OL,11,Fover alleged collusion in their
OL,12,Fkillings.JJim Loughrey and John
OL,13,FToland, both aged 36, were shot dead
OL,14,Fby the UDA within days of each other
OL,15,Fin the Co Londonderry villages of
OL,16,FGreysteel and Eglinton.
