OL,6,FIn court on Monday their barrister,
OL,7,FRonan Lavery KC, confirmed that
OL,8,Fconfidential settlements have been
OL,9,Freached in both actions.JThe
OL,10,Fdefendants are to pay the two widows'
OL,11,Flegal costs as part of the
OL,12,Fresolutions, which involve no
OL,13,Fadmission of liability.J"It's been a
OL,14,Flong time coming," Mr Lavery said.
OL,15,FWith family members of the two victims
OL,16,Fpresent in court, the judge
OL,17,Fcongratulated them for achieving the
OL,18,Foutcome.
