OL,6,FMr Justice Humphreys told them: "These
OL,7,Fare always difficult matters.J"The
OL,8,Fcourts have very many cases involving
OL,9,Fevents that happened years ago, where
OL,10,Fefforts are made to try and find out
OL,11,Fwhat happened in the deaths of loved
OL,12,Fones.J"That is a very difficult and
OL,13,Femotional trial for families to go
OL,14,Fthrough, but with the help of your
OL,15,Flawyers you have managed to reach a
OL,16,Fconclusion that is satisfactory."JHe
OL,17,Fadded: "By achieving a settlement what
OL,18,Fyou have done is bring finality to a
OL,19,Flengthy and difficult process."
